<codeline lineno="6"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="7"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>MetricTemplate_intro<sp/>Introduction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`MetricTemplate`<sp/>class,<sp/>implemented<sp/>in<sp/>Cython,<sp/>serves<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>robust<sp/>and<sp/>high-performance<sp/>base<sp/>for<sp/>defining<sp/>and<sp/>calculating<sp/>various<sp/>metrics<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>AnalysisG<sp/>framework.<sp/>It<sp/>is<sp/>specifically<sp/>designed<sp/>to<sp/>handle<sp/>the<sp/>complex<sp/>task<sp/>of<sp/>interpreting<sp/>and<sp/>processing<sp/>data<sp/>from<sp/>ROOT<sp/>files,<sp/>often<sp/>generated<sp/>in<sp/>high-energy<sp/>physics<sp/>experiments.<sp/>This<sp/>class<sp/>provides<sp/>mechanisms<sp/>for<sp/>managing<sp/>run<sp/>names,<sp/>variables,<sp/>and<sp/>a<sp/>sophisticated<sp/>`InterpretROOT`<sp/>method<sp/>that<sp/>leverages<sp/>parallel<sp/>processing<sp/>for<sp/>efficient<sp/>data<sp/>extraction<sp/>and<sp/>metric<sp/>computation.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="9"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="10"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>MetricTemplate_class<sp/>The<sp/>MetricTemplate<sp/>Class</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="11"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>`MetricTemplate`<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class`,<sp/>indicating<sp/>its<sp/>nature<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type.<sp/>This<sp/>allows<sp/>for<sp/>direct<sp/>and<sp/>optimized<sp/>interaction<sp/>with<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>data<sp/>structures<sp/>and<sp/>algorithms,<sp/>crucial<sp/>for<sp/>performance-intensive<sp/>tasks<sp/>like<sp/>ROOT<sp/>file<sp/>I/O<sp/>and<sp/>data<sp/>processing.<sp/>It<sp/>encapsulates<sp/>a<sp/>C++<sp/>`metric_template`<sp/>object<sp/>and<sp/>provides<sp/>a<sp/>Python-friendly<sp/>interface<sp/>to<sp/>its<sp/>functionalities.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="12"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="13"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>MetricTemplate_cinit_dealloc<sp/>Constructors<sp/>and<sp/>Destructors</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="14"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__cinit__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="15"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Cython<sp/>&quot;constructor&quot;<sp/>equivalent,<sp/>called<sp/>during<sp/>object<sp/>allocation.<sp/>It<sp/>initializes<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>C++<sp/>`metric_template`<sp/>object<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>its<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>`self.mtx`.<sp/>It<sp/>also<sp/>initializes<sp/>`self.root_leaves`<sp/>and<sp/>`self.root_fx`<sp/>as<sp/>empty<sp/>Python<sp/>dictionaries,<sp/>which<sp/>are<sp/>used<sp/>to<sp/>configure<sp/>ROOT<sp/>file<sp/>interpretation.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="16"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="17"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__init__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="18"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>standard<sp/>Python<sp/>initializer,<sp/>intentionally<sp/>left<sp/>empty<sp/>as<sp/>primary<sp/>initialization<sp/>is<sp/>handled<sp/>by<sp/>`__cinit__`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="19"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="20"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__dealloc__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="21"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Cython<sp/>&quot;destructor&quot;<sp/>equivalent,<sp/>called<sp/>upon<sp/>object<sp/>deallocation.<sp/>It<sp/>deallocates<sp/>the<sp/>C++<sp/>`metric_template`<sp/>object<sp/>pointed<sp/>to<sp/>by<sp/>`self.mtx`,<sp/>ensuring<sp/>proper<sp/>memory<sp/>cleanup.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="22"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="23"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>MetricTemplate_special_methods<sp/>Special<sp/>Methods</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="24"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__name__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="25"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>Returns<sp/>the<sp/>name<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>metric<sp/>object<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Python<sp/>string,<sp/>using<sp/>the<sp/>`env`<sp/>utility<sp/>function<sp/>for<sp/>conversion.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="26"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="27"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>MetricTemplate_properties<sp/>Properties</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="28"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>These<sp/>properties<sp/>provide<sp/>controlled<sp/>access<sp/>to<sp/>the<sp/>configuration<sp/>and<sp/>state<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>`MetricTemplate`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="29"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="30"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`@property<sp/>RunNames`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="31"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>Retrieves<sp/>a<sp/>dictionary<sp/>of<sp/>run<sp/>names<sp/>(C++<sp/>`map&lt;string,<sp/>string&gt;`)<sp/>associated<sp/>with<sp/>the<sp/>metric.<sp/>The<sp/>C++<sp/>map<sp/>is<sp/>converted<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>Python<sp/>dictionary<sp/>using<sp/>`as_basic_dict`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="32"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>`@RunNames.setter<sp/>RunNames(self,<sp/>dict<sp/>val)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="33"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>Sets<sp/>the<sp/>run<sp/>names.<sp/>The<sp/>input<sp/>Python<sp/>dictionary<sp/>`val`<sp/>is<sp/>converted<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>C++<sp/>`map&lt;string,<sp/>string&gt;`<sp/>using<sp/>`as_map`<sp/>and<sp/>assigned<sp/>to<sp/>`self.mtx.run_names`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="34"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="35"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`@property<sp/>Variables`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="36"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>Retrieves<sp/>a<sp/>list<sp/>of<sp/>variables<sp/>(C++<sp/>`vector&lt;string&gt;`)<sp/>managed<sp/>by<sp/>the<sp/>metric.<sp/>The<sp/>C++<sp/>vector<sp/>is<sp/>converted<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>Python<sp/>list<sp/>using<sp/>`env_vec`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="37"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>`@Variables.setter<sp/>Variables(self,<sp/>list<sp/>val)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="38"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>Sets<sp/>the<sp/>list<sp/>of<sp/>variables.<sp/>The<sp/>input<sp/>Python<sp/>list<sp/>`val`<sp/>is<sp/>converted<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>C++<sp/>`vector&lt;string&gt;`<sp/>using<sp/>`enc_list`<sp/>and<sp/>assigned<sp/>to<sp/>`self.mtx.variables`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="39"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="40"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>MetricTemplate_methods<sp/>Methods</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="41"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`Postprocessing(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="42"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>An<sp/>empty<sp/>placeholder<sp/>method<sp/>intended<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>overridden<sp/>by<sp/>subclasses<sp/>for<sp/>any<sp/>post-processing<sp/>steps<sp/>required<sp/>after<sp/>metric<sp/>calculation.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="43"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="44"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`InterpretROOT(self,<sp/>str<sp/>path,<sp/>list<sp/>epochs<sp/>=<sp/>[],<sp/>list<sp/>kfolds<sp/>=<sp/>[])`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="45"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>This<sp/>is<sp/>the<sp/>core<sp/>method<sp/>for<sp/>interpreting<sp/>and<sp/>processing<sp/>data<sp/>from<sp/>ROOT<sp/>files.<sp/>It<sp/>orchestrates<sp/>the<sp/>reading<sp/>of<sp/>ROOT<sp/>files,<sp/>filtering<sp/>by<sp/>epochs<sp/>and<sp/>k-folds,<sp/>and<sp/>applying<sp/>user-defined<sp/>functions<sp/>(`root_fx`)<sp/>to<sp/>extracted<sp/>data.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="46"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Parameters**:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="47"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>`path`<sp/>(str):<sp/>The<sp/>path<sp/>to<sp/>the<sp/>ROOT<sp/>file(s).<sp/>Can<sp/>be<sp/>a<sp/>directory,<sp/>a<sp/>specific<sp/>`.root`<sp/>file,<sp/>or<sp/>a<sp/>path<sp/>ending<sp/>with<sp/>`/`<sp/>(which<sp/>implies<sp/>`/*`).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="48"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>`epochs`<sp/>(list,<sp/>optional):<sp/>A<sp/>list<sp/>of<sp/>epoch<sp/>numbers<sp/>to<sp/>filter<sp/>the<sp/>ROOT<sp/>files.<sp/>Defaults<sp/>to<sp/>an<sp/>empty<sp/>list<sp/>(no<sp/>filtering).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="49"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>`kfolds`<sp/>(list,<sp/>optional):<sp/>A<sp/>list<sp/>of<sp/>k-fold<sp/>numbers<sp/>to<sp/>filter<sp/>the<sp/>ROOT<sp/>files.<sp/>Defaults<sp/>to<sp/>an<sp/>empty<sp/>list<sp/>(no<sp/>filtering).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="50"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Functionality**:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="51"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Configuration<sp/>Check**:<sp/>Verifies<sp/>that<sp/>`self.root_leaves`<sp/>(a<sp/>dictionary<sp/>mapping<sp/>tree<sp/>names<sp/>to<sp/>lists<sp/>of<sp/>leaves)<sp/>and<sp/>`self.root_fx`<sp/>(a<sp/>dictionary<sp/>mapping<sp/>tree/leaf<sp/>names<sp/>to<sp/>functions)<sp/>are<sp/>properly<sp/>set.<sp/>If<sp/>not,<sp/>it<sp/>logs<sp/>failure<sp/>messages<sp/>and<sp/>returns<sp/>`self`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="52"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Path<sp/>Normalization**:<sp/>Adjusts<sp/>the<sp/>`path`<sp/>argument<sp/>to<sp/>ensure<sp/>it&apos;s<sp/>suitable<sp/>for<sp/>file<sp/>globbing<sp/>(e.g.,<sp/>adds<sp/>`*`<sp/>if<sp/>it&apos;s<sp/>a<sp/>directory).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="53"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**File<sp/>Filtering**:<sp/>Uses<sp/>`self.ptr.ls`<sp/>(a<sp/>C++<sp/>function)<sp/>to<sp/>list<sp/>ROOT<sp/>files<sp/>and<sp/>then<sp/>filters<sp/>them<sp/>based<sp/>on<sp/>provided<sp/>`epochs`<sp/>and<sp/>`kfolds`.<sp/>`prange`<sp/>is<sp/>used<sp/>for<sp/>parallel<sp/>processing<sp/>of<sp/>file<sp/>paths.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="54"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Data<sp/>Structure<sp/>Initialization**:<sp/>Initializes<sp/>various<sp/>C++<sp/>maps<sp/>and<sp/>vectors<sp/>(`idx_map`,<sp/>`endx`,<sp/>`pause`,<sp/>`lsx`,<sp/>`mxf`,<sp/>`mapfx`,<sp/>`mapdx`,<sp/>`mapx`)<sp/>to<sp/>manage<sp/>file<sp/>indexing,<sp/>processing<sp/>state,<sp/>and<sp/>data<sp/>mapping.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="55"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Leaf<sp/>and<sp/>Function<sp/>Mapping**:<sp/>Iterates<sp/>through<sp/>`self.root_leaves`<sp/>and<sp/>`self.root_fx`<sp/>to<sp/>build<sp/>internal<sp/>mappings<sp/>(`mapfx`,<sp/>`mapdx`)<sp/>that<sp/>link<sp/>ROOT<sp/>tree/leaf<sp/>combinations<sp/>to<sp/>their<sp/>corresponding<sp/>processing<sp/>functions.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="56"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**ROOT<sp/>I/O<sp/>Setup**:<sp/>Initializes<sp/>an<sp/>`IO`<sp/>object<sp/>(presumably<sp/>from<sp/>`AnalysisG.core.io`)<sp/>with<sp/>the<sp/>filtered<sp/>ROOT<sp/>file<sp/>paths.<sp/>It<sp/>configures<sp/>the<sp/>`IO`<sp/>object<sp/>with<sp/>the<sp/>`Trees`<sp/>and<sp/>`Leaves`<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>read<sp/>based<sp/>on<sp/>`self.root_leaves`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="57"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Iterative<sp/>Data<sp/>Processing<sp/>Loop**:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="58"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Enters<sp/>a<sp/>`while<sp/>keep_going`<sp/>loop<sp/>to<sp/>iteratively<sp/>read<sp/>and<sp/>process<sp/>data<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>ROOT<sp/>files.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="59"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Metric<sp/>Function<sp/>Execution**:<sp/>For<sp/>each<sp/>configured<sp/>`root_fx`,<sp/>it<sp/>gathers<sp/>data<sp/>(`itx`)<sp/>and<sp/>calls<sp/>the<sp/>associated<sp/>function,<sp/>passing<sp/>`self`,<sp/>the<sp/>extracted<sp/>data,<sp/>and<sp/>metadata<sp/>(epoch,<sp/>kfold,<sp/>filename).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="60"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**File<sp/>Advancement**:<sp/>Uses<sp/>`prange`<sp/>to<sp/>advance<sp/>the<sp/>internal<sp/>pointers<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>`data_t`<sp/>objects<sp/>(representing<sp/>entries<sp/>in<sp/>ROOT<sp/>trees)<sp/>for<sp/>all<sp/>active<sp/>files.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="61"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Metadata<sp/>Extraction**:<sp/>Extracts<sp/>metadata<sp/>like<sp/>`kfold`,<sp/>`epoch`,<sp/>and<sp/>`model_name`<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>current<sp/>file<sp/>path.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="62"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Progress<sp/>Reporting**:<sp/>Updates<sp/>a<sp/>progress<sp/>bar<sp/>(`iox.prg`)<sp/>with<sp/>the<sp/>current<sp/>file<sp/>being<sp/>processed.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="63"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Pause/Unpause<sp/>Logic**:<sp/>Manages<sp/>`pause`<sp/>and<sp/>`endx`<sp/>flags<sp/>to<sp/>control<sp/>which<sp/>files<sp/>are<sp/>actively<sp/>being<sp/>read<sp/>and<sp/>when<sp/>a<sp/>file<sp/>has<sp/>been<sp/>fully<sp/>processed.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="64"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Loop<sp/>Termination**:<sp/>The<sp/>loop<sp/>continues<sp/>as<sp/>long<sp/>as<sp/>`keep_going`<sp/>is<sp/>true,<sp/>which<sp/>is<sp/>set<sp/>to<sp/>false<sp/>when<sp/>all<sp/>files<sp/>have<sp/>been<sp/>fully<sp/>processed.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="65"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Postprocessing<sp/>Call**:<sp/>After<sp/>the<sp/>main<sp/>processing<sp/>loop,<sp/>it<sp/>calls<sp/>`self.Postprocessing()`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="66"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Return<sp/>Value**:<sp/>Returns<sp/>`self`<sp/>for<sp/>method<sp/>chaining.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="67"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
