<codeline lineno="69"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>`MetricTemplate`<sp/>extensively<sp/>uses<sp/>Cython&apos;s<sp/>capabilities<sp/>to<sp/>bridge<sp/>Python<sp/>and<sp/>C++:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="70"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class<sp/>MetricTemplate`:<sp/>Declares<sp/>it<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type.</highlight></codeline>
