<codeline lineno="73"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`from<sp/>AnalysisG.core.tools<sp/>cimport<sp/>*`,<sp/>`from<sp/>AnalysisG.core.meta<sp/>cimport<sp/>*`,<sp/>`from<sp/>AnalysisG.core.structs<sp/>cimport<sp/>*`:<sp/>Imports<sp/>C++<sp/>declarations<sp/>from<sp/>corresponding<sp/>`.pxd`<sp/>files.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="74"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`cython.parallel.prange`:<sp/>Enables<sp/>parallel<sp/>execution<sp/>of<sp/>loops,<sp/>leveraging<sp/>multiple<sp/>CPU<sp/>cores<sp/>for<sp/>faster<sp/>processing.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="75"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`cython.operator.dereference<sp/>as<sp/>deref`:<sp/>Used<sp/>to<sp/>dereference<sp/>C++<sp/>pointers.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="76"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`env`,<sp/>`enc`,<sp/>`env_vec`,<sp/>`enc_list`,<sp/>`as_basic_dict`,<sp/>`as_map`:<sp/>Utility<sp/>functions<sp/>(likely<sp/>from<sp/>`AnalysisG.core.tools`)<sp/>for<sp/>converting<sp/>between<sp/>Python<sp/>and<sp/>C++<sp/>data<sp/>types<sp/>(strings,<sp/>lists,<sp/>dictionaries,<sp/>vectors,<sp/>maps).</highlight></codeline>
